{"tid":1659717,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"李顯龍稱香港「五大訴求」旨在羞辱及推翻特區政府","createTime":"2019-10-17T06:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T09:10:22.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee882666a9d3227f0a7a3bc40bf89b2928c68527","tid":1659717,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"香港反修例示威浪潮持續，引起國際社會關注。新加坡總理李顯龍周三（16日）罕有強硬表示，香港示威者提出的「五大訴求」，旨在羞辱及推翻香港特區政府。<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍在一個商業會議致詞時稱，香港示威者的訴求是為了令港府蒙羞及倒台。他說︰「此事沒簡單解決方法，他們要求普選，但香港不是一個國家，而是一個特別行政區。」他指新加坡政府關注香港局勢，又認為香港出現麻煩、示威甚至騷亂，對香港來說都是非常可惜。<br />\n<br />\n此外，李顯龍周二（15日）出席活動時也談到香港，指新加坡的情況不同，但不能完全避開這種撕裂社會的勢力。他稱：「若這類事情發生在我們身上，我們需要承擔一樣甚至更惡劣的後果，因為我們更脆弱。」他認為港府沒有正視市民對經濟及社會的關切，導致示威及暴力升級。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191016/bkn-20191016233808810-1016_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191016%2Fbkn-20191016233808810-1016_00822_001.html&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgAFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=6cf0d7de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191016/bkn-20191016233808810-1016_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3d188dbe0b3942a27b2183b79f57ecc75048652e","tid":1659717,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3c2ce68a24f2b56bd67cedb1918006f73cfb0042","tid":1659717,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> IG &ldquo;bye bye starbucks&rdquo; challenge</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659200</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手推啦各位，和理非出嚟啦。"},{"pid":"8f31d37184c49424cd6c42a921f218291f7f558f","tid":1659717,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"講穿了，新加坡只是一個講英文和可以自由「信神」的中共國"},{"pid":"a29e1f364a5a1057e92902645cec6f692e0cc9cd","tid":1659717,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:12:26.000Z","msg":"李光耀之後 新加坡再冇能人！"},{"pid":"2a4ccd8d6c612b7c3d2b5e7db0479b19f069e7bb","tid":1659717,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"pull"},{"pid":"de3f2015df6e676325f89226b8f2dfcde7270244","tid":1659717,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"不要干涉外國事務."}]}